summary: An ordinance authorizing the dismissal of the suit instituted by the City of Seattle for the condemnation, appropriation and taking of land and other property for general municipal purposes, as provided in Section 2 of Ordinance No. 40571, as amended by Ordinance No. 41404, Cause No. 144881, of the Superior Court of the State of Washington, in and for King County, insofar as the same affects certain property.
